  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Activated Recombinant Human Factor VII in Haemophilia Patients With Inhibitors During and After Major Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-Label, Randomized, Parallel, Multicenter Trial Comparing the Safety and Efficacy of rFVIIa When Administered as i.v. Bolus or i.v. Continuous Infusion to Hemophiliacs With Inhibitors During and After Major Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
